Φ(Expectancy_Value) = σ(expectancy|success-probability) ∘ λ(value|cost-benefit-appraisal) ∘ ρ(importance|personal-significance) ∘ μ(utility|instrumentality) → [κ(motivation)] → [✶(achievement-behavior)] + ε | :motivational

