                              CROSS-THEORY RESONANCE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

With Attribution Theory (L044):
    Attribution patterns shape expectancy beliefs
    Causal locus → Self-concept → Expectancy
    
With Self-Determination Theory (L015):
    Competence need ↔ Expectancy beliefs
    Autonomy need ↔ Intrinsic value
    Relatedness need ↔ Attainment value
    
With Self-Efficacy (P001):
    Self-efficacy ⊂ Expectancy beliefs
    Domain-specific confidence feeds into general expectancy
    
With Growth Mindset (P002):
    Incremental theory → Higher expectancy through effort attributions
    Entity theory → Lower expectancy, ability-focused

